        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-23" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,1,0&quot;&gt;Atletas, Encarregados de Educação, Treinadores, Staff e Gerência&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-24" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;O sistema deve permitir a criação, edição e consulta de perfis para todos os intervenientes do clube. A&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;visualização e edição das informações (pessoais, desportivas e médicas) devem ser controladas de forma&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;dinâmica, dependendo estritamente do nível de acesso e do cargo (perfil de segurança) do utilizador&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;autenticado." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="1260" x="491" y="-340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-25" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Nome do Requisito" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-26" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Ator Principal" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-399" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-27" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Descrição" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="280" x="210" y="-340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-28" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Prioridade" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-29" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pré-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="280" x="210" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-30" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pós-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="280" x="210" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="280" x="210" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Alta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema de controlo de acessos baseado em papéis (RBAC - &lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;62&quot;&gt;Role-Based Access Control&lt;/i&gt;) tem de estar&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;configurado.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. Para a visualização ou edição de perfis de terceiros, o utilizador tem de estar autenticado e possuir os&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;privilégios necessários (ex: um Treinador tem de estar associado à equipa do Atleta que pretende consultar).&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="1260" x="491" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. Os dados do perfil são persistidos na base de dados com a devida encriptação em campos sensíveis&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;(ex: passwords, dados médicos).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. É gerado um registo de auditoria (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;37&quot;&gt;log&lt;/i&gt;) interno documentando quem criou ou alterou o perfil e a respetiva&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;data/hora.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O perfil fica disponível ou restrito nas listagens globais do clube, conforme as regras de negócio&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;associadas ao seu papel.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="280" width="1260" x="490" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema deve garantir que um atleta/encarregado apenas consegue editar os seus próprios dados&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;pessoais.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A interface deve bloquear a visualização de dados financeiros (ex: quotas) aos Treinadores, limitando o&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;acesso a esses campos estritamente à Gerência/Secretaria e ao próprio Atleta.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. A criação de contas com perfis de nível superior (Gerência, Treinadores) deve ser obrigatoriamente&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;aprovada ou realizada por um Administrador do sistema.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="1260" x="491" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
